<br>
<br>
Creapiing stood on a boulder, next to the shore of the lake, and spread her arms wide.  She forced her body to become as rigid as death.  Then slowly, to the outcry of the crowd, she allowed herself to fall.<br>
<br>
Red gore, blood, ink, boiled up behind her and clouded the water.  <br>
<br>
The procession stood uncertain for a moment, then one brave Teir'dal jumped into the water.  The splash awoke the charmed onlookers.  Many jumped .  With each addition the water stirred the redness more until the children of Innoruuk floated in a sea of blood.<br>
